{"title":"字典","date":"2019-08-09T15:30:38.000Z","link":"post/字典","tags":["字典"],"categories":["python"],"updated":"2019-08-11T22:29:55.419Z","content":"<h4 id=\"列表用-，元组用-，字典用\">列表用[]，元组用()，字典用{}<a href=\"post/字典#列表用-，元组用-，字典用\"></a></h4><p>字典，可以存储两种相关的信息，并根据key可以调用value</p>\n<h2 id=\"定义一个简单字典\">定义一个简单字典<a href=\"post/字典#定义一个简单字典\"></a></h2><p>字典初始化方式，字典名称 = {‘key’：‘value’，}</p>\n<p>注：key与value之间用（：）隔开</p>\n<p>实例：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/字典/1.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p>运行结果：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/字典/2.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"添加键值对\">添加键值对<a href=\"post/字典#添加键值对\"></a></h2><p>字典名[‘key] = value</p>\n<p>将一对新键值添加到字典</p>\n<p>实例：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/字典/3.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p>运行结果：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/字典/4.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p>小结：添加键值对是依次添加到字典，也可先创建一个空字典，然后逐个添加键值。</p>\n<h2 id=\"修改字典中的值\">修改字典中的值<a href=\"post/字典#修改字典中的值\"></a></h2><p>字典名[’键‘] = ’新值‘</p>\n<p>将键相关联的值改为新值</p>\n<p>实例：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/字典/5.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p>运行结果：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/字典/6.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p>小结：可用for语句遍历，整体修改字典值</p>\n<h2 id=\"删除键值对\">删除键值对<a href=\"post/字典#删除键值对\"></a></h2><p>字典中不需要的信息，可用</p>\n<p>del 字典名[‘键’]</p>\n<p>删除一对键值</p>\n<p>实例：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/字典/7.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p>运行结果：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/字典/8.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"遍历字典\">遍历字典<a href=\"post/字典#遍历字典\"></a></h2><p>当字典中键值过多时，可用for语句遍历字典中信息，可单独查看键或值</p>\n<p>.items()函数会返回一个键值对列表</p>\n<p>实例：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">user_0 = &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">'username'</span>: <span class=\"string\">'efermi'</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">'first'</span>: <span class=\"string\">'enrico'</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">'last'</span>: <span class=\"string\">'fermi'</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> key, value <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> user_0.items():</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(<span class=\"string\">\"\\nKey: \"</span> + key)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(<span class=\"string\">\"Value: \"</span> + value + <span class=\"string\">\"\\n\"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>运行结果：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/字典/9.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p>小结：键值中注意（，）分隔，for语句注意（：）</p>\n<h2 id=\"遍历字典中的键\">遍历字典中的键<a href=\"post/字典#遍历字典中的键\"></a></h2><p>当检查字典中的键或不使用值时，可用</p>\n<p>.key()函数，只返回字典中键</p>\n<p>实例：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">favorite_language = &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">'jen'</span>: <span class=\"string\">'python'</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">'sarah'</span>: <span class=\"string\">'c'</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">'edward'</span>: <span class=\"string\">'ruby'</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">'phil'</span>: <span class=\"string\">'python'</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> name <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> favorite_language.keys():</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(name.title() + <span class=\"string\">'\\n'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">friends = [<span class=\"string\">'phil'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'sarah'</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> name <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> favorite_language.keys():</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(name.title())</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> name <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> friends:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        print(<span class=\"string\">\" hi \"</span> + name.title() + <span class=\"string\">\", I see your favorite language is \"</span> + favorite_language[name].title() + <span class=\"string\">\"!\"</span> + <span class=\"string\">'\\n'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>运行结果：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/字典/10.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"按顺序遍历字典中所有键\">按顺序遍历字典中所有键<a href=\"post/字典#按顺序遍历字典中所有键\"></a></h2><p>获取特定顺序返回元素，可以在for循环中对返回的键进行排序。</p>\n<p>.sorted()函数</p>\n<p>实例：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> kk <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> sorted(favorite_language.keys()):</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(kk.title() + <span class=\"string\">', thank you for taking the poll'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>运行结果：</p>\n<p><img src=\"/post/字典/11.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"遍历字典中所有的值\">遍历字典中所有的值<a href=\"post/字典#遍历字典中所有的值\"></a></h2><p>与遍历键方法相同，使用</p>\n<p>.values()函数来返回一个值的列表，不包含任何键</p>\n<p>实例：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> iii <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> set(favorite_language.values()):</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(iii.title())</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"剔除字典中重复项\">剔除字典中重复项<a href=\"post/字典#剔除字典中重复项\"></a></h2><p>遍历键值时，会出现很多重复项，不方便审阅</p>\n<p>.set()函数剔除多余重复项</p>\n<p>实例：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">print(<span class=\"string\">'The following languages have been mentioned:'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> iii <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> set(favorite_language.values()):</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(iii.title())</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"字典中存储字典或列表\">字典中存储字典或列表<a href=\"post/字典#字典中存储字典或列表\"></a></h2><p>当字典中每个值还需存储键值时，可在字典中再次嵌套字典，当每个键对应多个值时，可在字典中嵌套列表。</p>\n<p>实例：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pizza = &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">'crust'</span>: <span class=\"string\">'thick'</span>,</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">'toppings'</span>: [<span class=\"string\">'mushrooms'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'extracheese'</span>],</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(<span class=\"string\">'you ordered a '</span> + pizza[<span class=\"string\">'crust'</span>] + <span class=\"string\">'-crust pizza'</span> + <span class=\"string\">\"with the following toppings:\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> topping <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> pizza[<span class=\"string\">'toppings'</span>]:</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(<span class=\"string\">'\\t'</span> + topping)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">favorite_language = &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">'jen'</span>: [<span class=\"string\">'python'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'ruby'</span>],</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">'sarah'</span>: [<span class=\"string\">'c'</span>],</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">'edward'</span>: [<span class=\"string\">'ruby'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'go'</span>],</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"string\">'phil'</span>: [<span class=\"string\">'python'</span>, <span class=\"string\">'haskell'</span>],</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> name, languages <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> favorite_language.items():</span><br><span class=\"line\">    print(name.title() + <span class=\"string\">':'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> language <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> languages:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        print(<span class=\"string\">'\\t'</span>+ language.title())</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<p>字典嵌套字典方法与嵌套列表相同。</p>\n<h2 id=\"总结\">总结<a href=\"post/字典#总结\"></a></h2><p>本章学习了如何初始化一个字典，字典的键值访问和使用，和字典与列表的嵌套。</p>\n","prev":{"title":"输入","link":"post/输入"},"next":{"title":"if语句","link":"post/if语句"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/post/字典/","toc":[{"title":"定义一个简单字典","id":"定义一个简单字典","index":"1"},{"title":"添加键值对","id":"添加键值对","index":"2"},{"title":"修改字典中的值","id":"修改字典中的值","index":"3"},{"title":"删除键值对","id":"删除键值对","index":"4"},{"title":"遍历字典","id":"遍历字典","index":"5"},{"title":"遍历字典中的键","id":"遍历字典中的键","index":"6"},{"title":"按顺序遍历字典中所有键","id":"按顺序遍历字典中所有键","index":"7"},{"title":"遍历字典中所有的值","id":"遍历字典中所有的值","index":"8"},{"title":"剔除字典中重复项","id":"剔除字典中重复项","index":"9"},{"title":"字典中存储字典或列表","id":"字典中存储字典或列表","index":"10"},{"title":"总结","id":"总结","index":"11"}]}